NAME
  User manager
  
SYNOPSIS
  user add <user>
  user remove <user>
  user list

DESCRIPTION
  The application for user management.

OPTIONS
  list
    Returns list of all known users.
  
  add
    For creating a new user. Password and Role will be required in the next steps.
    
  remove
    It removes a user from system.

EXAMPLES
  user list
    Returns list of all available packages..

  user add tonda
    It creates user "tonda".
    
  user remove pepa
    it removes user "pepa" from system.